{"tid":1486240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不割蓆，不分化，不篤灰","createTime":"2019-08-18T21:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T02:28:47.000Z","uid":60740,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"85b6bb1658f6fd43ca37b36099e2f5b8b2e50eb2","tid":1486240,"uid":60740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T21:40:35.000Z","msg":"核彈都路割之後就到左分化考驗<br />\n一人少句兄弟爬山<br />\n有咩就睇返天琦<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVEUhAVki0DA&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=4048bd29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA</a><br />\n我地唔要教條主義<br />\n所以要有勇武<br />\n唔係話對方有咩唔可以做<br />\n可以行嘅路唔係得自己個條<br />\n所以要兄弟爬山各自修行<br />\n但勇武嘅兄弟都要留意返做事要因事制宜<br />\n不流血，不被捕 be water<br />\n記住我地不割蓆不分化不篤灰"},{"pid":"4af3a5ffc96c0c90f5785cfe79df7c3e22514eaf","tid":1486240,"uid":258578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T21:41:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"539349021b029de557820245e30e846cbce270af","tid":1486240,"uid":60740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T21:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bf30e5970966270d9376a3b7ec350f96d2ec6d","tid":1486240,"uid":118350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T21:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1a37a275facf5b64c9774ce007cc68256800c7","tid":1486240,"uid":60740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T21:46:16.000Z","msg":"想同和理非講我地唔要教條主義同兄弟爬山<br />\n想同勇武手足講我地要因時制宜"},{"pid":"26a59f6c99bca693433a6644b77f62aa7d2ce7f7","tid":1486240,"uid